item.title: CVE-2018-5503|2024-09-16T17:23:05.265Z -- f5%20networks%2C%20inc. -- big-ip%20%28pem%29
item.description: On F5 BIG-IP versions 13.0.0 - 13.1.0.3 or 12.0.0 - 12.1.3.1, TMM may restart when processing a specifically crafted page through a virtual server with an associated PEM policy that has content insertion as an action.
